Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:09.01,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}I had lost my way during my journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:17.02,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Only my soul was wandering, while I stood still.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.02,0:00:25.28,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}But right now, I'm walking to a distant place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:33.53,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}That's right, ever since I met you on this road.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:41.96,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}The travellers witnessed the song, the forbidden song,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:52.72,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}And I became attached to it as I heard it alone with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.72,0:01:00.81,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}If the world I saw in my dreams exists somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:09.20,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Let's go search for it, beyond the winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:13.37,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Whether it's a freezing dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:17.58,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}A dry midday,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:21.75,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}A shivering night,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.75,0:01:28.00,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}or the ends of the Earth, let's go and see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.95,0:01:45.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.24,0:01:49.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a little is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:01:56.23,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.23,0:02:01.20,Chapter Name Title Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Wolf and the Great Plan
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:19.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure came back early.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.21,0:02:46.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.32,0:02:48.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:03:01.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to collect three Rumione.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.15,0:03:03.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There's forty-four Rumione left, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.61,0:03:06.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:10.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,All I could think of was to take that money and go to a gambling den.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:14.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure you have more talent for gambling than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.53,0:03:18.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's not going to end well at this rate, then the person who uses it will be the winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:23.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like anything will change, even if I gathered the three Rumione towards my debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:04.86,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:07.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:11.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:19.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I dropped this from the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:22.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:25.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:27.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:29.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "Sorry?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:31.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you "sorry" about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:35.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you do if I took that money and ran away?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:40.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've been fine with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:44.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of my mistake, I can't carry out the contract we made.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.69,0:04:47.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, at the least, it should be enough for traveling expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:49.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:52.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving me traveling expenses, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.99,0:04:57.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.53,0:04:59.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one at fault, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:01.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If I weren't with you, you could've borrowed money!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:04.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you angry because of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:06.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you blame me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:11.01,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You came with me because you were worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:13.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't possibly do-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.26,0:05:14.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:18.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:20.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:33.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn softy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.24,0:05:34.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Softy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:36.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:38.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I was selfish and followed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:42.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But that didn't work out, so you should be angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:48.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But you just brush away my hand and immediately apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:50.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:54.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I did something I can't take back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:56.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Something that I can't apologize enough for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:05:59.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I wanted to do what I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:04.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But if that backfired, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:06.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:09.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:14.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why are you such a... {tsundere}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:18.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Softy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:22.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my personality... I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.93,0:06:25.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.16,0:06:28.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Your personality? Your personality, you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:31.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a male's ability to know when to lie and charm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:32.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:34.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:37.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:41.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There are times where someone wants you to lie,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:45.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and times when you say it, they just want to jump onto your face and pulverize it. {tlc what what what}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:47.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What time do you think it is now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:50.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The... The latter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:54.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't believe it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:56.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an unbelievable softy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:07:01.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it'd be unfair to charm me in this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.80,0:07:04.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm shocked, if I say so myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:08.01,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I wanted you to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:09.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.38,0:07:17.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:20.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you such a softy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:23.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're special.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.12,0:07:48.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what the heck are we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:50.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one that made me do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:56.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was a good rehearsal for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:00.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:04.33,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you let me be angry next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:07.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy that you care for me and all,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.27,0:08:10.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,but there are times when problems are solved more quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:12.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,when we yell and get angry at each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:17.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.61,0:08:24.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, exactly how much money is in that leather pouch?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:27.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Three and two-sevenths Rumione.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:30.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, there's forty-three and five-sevenths left of your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:33.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a good plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.59,0:08:35.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:37.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be troublesome if you expected too much out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.57,0:08:42.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.24,0:08:43.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.43,0:08:46.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, we'd be captured right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:50.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's one thing that can be made possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:52.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.70,0:09:08.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:10.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:17.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have something important to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:21.01,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to take that road this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:24.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit out of place, but it should be fine if it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:29.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,With God's protection, haven't you been able to pass through them all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:31.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.81,0:09:38.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've heard that mercenaries have been appearing in that area recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.42,0:09:41.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,God will surely protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:43.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing to be concerned about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:45.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:48.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a wonderful shepherd.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:50.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We're very proud of you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:54.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Smuggle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:56.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.04,0:09:57.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:10:00.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being a fool, leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:05.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There have been people in the past who have tried to smuggle using the same method.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:07.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They were all captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:09.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you know, then there's nothing left to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.43,0:10:14.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,People on the verge of bankruptcy often mistake reckless plans for perfect ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:16.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's what you're doing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:21.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But what if there were a resourceful person we could fully trust to smuggle gold?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:30.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}If there's someone so resourceful, they wouldn't need to smuggle gold, they're already making enough profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:32.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just an empty theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.05,0:10:36.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What if the person is resourceful, but not making any profit at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:38.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:41.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of person would fall under that category?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:45.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Skilled, can be found in this city,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:48.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,has a small salary, and also needs money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:52.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This person is not satisfied with their employer,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:10:55.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and has an indistinct bitterness towards them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:10:59.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Their employer is the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:04.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Smuggling gold would be an act of defiance against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:06.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only would they gain money,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:09.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,but if we tempt them with being able to take revenge on the church,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:12.01,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they would come biting for the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.68,0:11:16.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, the chance of them betraying us is nearly zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:21.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to tell you the name of this person, I'm sure you would understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:28.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you two just smuggle gold yourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:33.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just odd to come to us, since your share of the profits would be lower.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.06,0:11:35.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the last day to pay my debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:39.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the sun sets, I will be captured by the Trading Guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:43.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, this is all the money I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.00,0:11:49.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to take this as insurance and believe in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:50.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:54.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,To suspend the debt collection,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.37,0:11:58.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and to collects funds to invest in the smuggling of gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:02.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:05.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have time to be hesitating?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:06.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:07.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:11.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems another one just left now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.72,0:12:15.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,My ears are especially good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:16.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can clearly hear whisperings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:21.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They're making plans downstairs so that they can run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:24.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, another one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.29,0:12:28.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, if the company continues to do nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.25,0:12:29.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.51,0:12:33.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister Remerio, how about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.78,0:12:38.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you know the routes to sell smuggled gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:42.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The conditions aren't bad, so won't you join us in smuggling gold?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:45.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister Remerio!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:48.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:50.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.51,0:12:54.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,May God watch over us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:02.86,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Call in Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:03.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.09,0:13:13.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, it's my turn next.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:14.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:20.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me, is a good-natured person like you going to trick that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:25.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There are good-natured and pure people in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:28.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty arrogant for someone who doesn't know a thing about females.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:33.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you corner Remerio during our negotiation earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:39.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk to her myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.89,0:13:43.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it was me that got lost in greed and got a hold of those goods in decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:48.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have you talking for me just because I feel depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:51.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I thought I'd have you owe me one,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.90,0:13:54.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and have you pay me back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.28,0:13:56.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.43,0:14:05.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:10.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Lawrence and... Horo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:17.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Meeting by chance in front of the church is no doubt the work of God!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.26,0:14:20.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't trick anyone with that, even me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.39,0:14:25.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There have been people recently who have been drinking the consecrated wine at the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.81,0:14:30.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't drink beer and I rarely ever touch wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.51,0:14:33.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:36.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I actually came to request a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:37.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.64,0:14:40.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:44.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's not stand around here and go to a stall. {a stand? tlc please}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:45.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.39,0:14:52.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,To our reunion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:03.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you said you could go to Ramtra, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:05.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:07.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Even while herding sheep?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:09.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's not too many.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:13.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to request a particularly strange job this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:15.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Your pay will be twenty Rumione.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:18.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it won't be just a cheap document,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:19.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:23.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:26.86,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Twenty?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:29.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:32.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is danger, so that's your pay if you succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:34.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you fail, you won't get paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.38,0:15:36.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:39.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Your job would be to herd the sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:43.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And, if possible, to bring them back safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.62,0:15:47.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't need any other skills except your skills as a shepherd.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:50.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be a very dangerous job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:52.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty Rumione is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.73,0:15:54.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't deny it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:15:58.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I won't forcefully request it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:16:00.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind if you think it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:06.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The cost to join the union, at the very most, is one Rumione, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:12.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}With twenty Rumione, you won't have to rent a house and you can work without worrying about living costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:15.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, you will be able to easily buy a license.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:19.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, you will be the female owner of Nora Tailors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:24.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you intend to join this city's tailoring and accessories union, Nora?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:28.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was thinking of joining in a different city.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.79,0:16:30.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:36.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The size of this city is charming, though, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.13,0:16:39.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to live in a city without your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:45.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But, well, you don't want to be involved with the church anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:47.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:53.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs37}You work diligently, and you protect the sheep the church entrusts you, but no matter how hard you persist,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:57.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,they continue to doubt whether you are using pagan magic or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:16:59.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:03.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And they are trying to reveal your true character
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.54,0:17:08.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,by making you go to places where no other shepherd would dare go,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:13.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,while saying other shepherds have already taken the other lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:20.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs37}I'm sure the priests will keep sending you off to dangerous lands until wolves or mercenaries attack you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:25.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And they'll keep sending you off every day until they have proof that you're a pagan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.26,0:17:29.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I was also in a very similar situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:31.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me say it clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:33.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The church here is lower than pigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.30,0:17:43.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is what we came up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:48.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll cause some trouble for the church, earn money, and go to a different city.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:49.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:52.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:55.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Smuggle gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:58.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:03.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But what can I possibly do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:07.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,To pass through this city's strict gates,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.26,0:18:10.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,we will hide gold within the stomachs of the sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:21.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I hear you out till the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.17,0:18:25.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In cities influenced by the church, all gold has an absurdly high price.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.97,0:18:31.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, the best supplier is the pagan city, Ramtra.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:36.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,However, by taking the safe road from Ramtra, there are too many people on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:41.45,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Additionally, that road is also the turf of many other shepherds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:46.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I am able to take a road that is sparsely populated,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:49.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,which will also serve to keep suspicions about what I am doing low.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:54.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, the road I take is the shortest distance between Ramtra and this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:55.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:19:00.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, you have been treated terribly by the church in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:05.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, this plan is also the perfect chance to show your resentment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:11.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The church's greatest source of funds come from donations and the export and import of gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:16.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if we're found, a terrible punishment will await us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:20.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, for your safety once the job finishes, you will need to leave the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:22.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.98,0:19:25.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The pay is twenty Rumione.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:43.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.19,0:19:47.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:49.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:50.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.64,0:19:52.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.87,0:19:57.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were a job from other people, I wouldn't accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:20:01.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I accepted because... it was you, Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:15.33,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you act more happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:17.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going well, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.70,0:20:21.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter the profit,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:25.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no gamble worth putting one's life on the line. {tell that to akagi and kaiji, bitch}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:26.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.59,0:20:32.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, that speech emphasizing the profit was the same as swindling her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.18,0:20:38.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's common sense among merchants that the one to accept an unfavorable contract is the stupid one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:40.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And look at the person we made a contract with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:43.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a shepherd who doesn't know her right from her left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:47.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's true that her smile did seem pure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.78,0:20:50.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:52.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a helpless softy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.16,0:21:00.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That shepherd girl is not a prey that's meant to be chased and eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.89,0:21:08.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a bold shepherd that jumped into a nest of wild beasts herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.67,0:21:13.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps she's wearing sheep's clothes, and might be another animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:16.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really want to say it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.69,0:21:20.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a shepherd that even I recognize.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.74,0:21:23.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.37,0:21:25.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep being a softy to a limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.73,0:21:31.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, anyway, it'll end in a way where all of us can laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.28,0:21:32.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice but to work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.70,0:21:34.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.42,0:21:38.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe chuckling with just us two alone is more charming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.12,0:21:41.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly is charming, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:45.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd feel more relieved to laugh with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.12,0:21:48.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a softy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:49.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.26,0:21:50.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:55.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.70,0:21:58.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we really going it do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.14,0:22:00.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.37,0:22:02.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.14,0:22:05.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do it, Liebert!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.86,0:22:19.84,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven apples on the witch's tree
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.84,0:22:25.22,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,With seven seeds to plant inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.22,0:22:30.40,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,In spring time I grew a magic song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.40,0:22:33.14,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Then skipping along,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.14,0:22:35.70,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I sang the song to everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:41.13,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I look at the world through apple eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.13,0:22:46.46,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And cut myself a slice of sunshine pie
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.46,0:22:51.80,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I danced with the peanuts for the flies
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:54.43,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Till someone had told me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.43,0:22:57.49,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,To say hello for every good-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.49,0:23:02.45,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Saw some sugar stars
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.45,0:23:07.54,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put them in a jar
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.54,0:23:10.11,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.11,0:23:13.55,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.55,0:23:17.41,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little wolf inside a cart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.41,0:23:18.76,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,You say,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.76,0:23:23.05,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And off I go from June to May
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.05,0:23:28.94,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.94,0:23:32.59,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.43,0:23:43.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Wolf and Young Pack
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.55,0:23:49.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Wolf and Young Pack
